                  <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d2"><locus target="#119v" facs="122">Fol. 119v</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1101GodtheFather">God the Father</ref> surrounded by the four Living Creatures</desc></decoNote>
                  <decoNote type="miniature" xml:id="d3"><locus target="#133v" facs="136">Fol. 133v</locus><desc><ref type="authFile" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/AT1035HolyMan">Holy Man Portrait</ref>,<persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS4585Georgeo">St George of Lydda</persName> and the <term key="dragon" ana="#dragon"/></desc></decoNote>
                  <decoNote type="frame" xml:id="d4">
                  Decorative designs:
                  <locus target="#1r #6v #67v #89v #120r" facs="003 009 070 092 122">folss. 1r, 6v, 67v, 89v, 120r, </locus> (ornamental band);
                  <locus target="#19r #27r #33v #38v #46r #55v #62v #78v #92r #97r #102v #113r #133r" facs="021 029 036 041 048 058 065 081 094 099 105 115 135">19r, 27r, 33v, 38v, 46r, 55v, 62v, 78v, 92r, 97r, 102v, 113r, 133r, </locus> (line of alternating red and black dots);
                  <locus target="#96r" facs="098">96r</locus> (multiple full stops)
                  </decoNote>
